name: Oregon Quail
description:
You and your flock must migrate south...  forever.

Slowly starving and lacking respite, you must steal to survive.

Fly as far as you can for a "high score."

An Arcade RPG created for mini jam 99 in RPG Maker MV by:

Celeste - Music & SFX & Design

Jacob - Coding & UI & Design

K.K. Dream - Art & Implementation & Design

Haley - Coding & Implementation & Design

NOTE: We are not responsible for hasty decisions regarding numbers which may have made this game crazy unbalanced
